Articles.Content:
Spaceplane "Kwhite Star".

Spaceplane in "White Star" style from "Babylon-5". Has good maneuverability, you can fly to the Mun or Minmus or just fly around KSC.

 Just a beautiful spaceplane, fly and enjoy without wasting words.

Yes ... no ladder, so as not to spoil the look:D

**Features:**

Version KSP - 0.90.0

Crew - 2 kerbals;

Number of pieces - 68;

Weight - 11.428t;

Fuel Capacity:

Fuel - 465;

Oxidizer - 385;

Power supply:

RITEG - 1;

The quantity of turbojet - 1;

The quantity of nuclear propulsion engines - 1 (clipped in turbojet);

DeltaV in orbit 72x72km - 2850-2900m/s.

**Control:**

8 - Turn on/off turbojet;

9 - Turn on/off intake;

0 - Turn on/off nuclear engine.

